name: Experiment Or Die #63
description: Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of personal assets. The path forward in life is rarely clear regardless if there are plenty of things guiding you. In the end you need to follow your gut and try and do what is going to make you happy. You may not be able to reveal your inner desires but do what you can to reach them anyway. Twitter and IG: Nikejerk
